  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/3889602004228a69c1770d4527993acc.avif?t=1728411903\" width=610 height=130 /></span><br><br>Slash your way through Estencel! Traverse across a corrupted, maze like city fighting horrors. Customize and arm yourself into the ultimate monster killing assassin in this fast paced dark fantasy Action. Solve the mysteries of this world before they swallow you whole.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/1fcfa6da0cf27d22722ed8f716d9f135.poster.avif?t=1728411903\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/1fcfa6da0cf27d22722ed8f716d9f135.webm?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/1fcfa6da0cf27d22722ed8f716d9f135.mp4?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A Variety of Enemies — Choose your combat style against diverse opponents and defeat merciless bosses with your cunning wit.<br><br></li><li>Exploration — Traverse the city and its outskirts and discover what secrets hide in its shadows.<br><br></li><li>Online multiplayer - play with your friends in co-op for up to 8 people.<br> </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/9b2d1b458e1abf5cea2be42c43850495.poster.avif?t=1728411903\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/9b2d1b458e1abf5cea2be42c43850495.webm?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/9b2d1b458e1abf5cea2be42c43850495.mp4?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic Combat System — Upgrade your primary weapon or swap to your secondary to overwhelm your opponent.<br><br></li><li>Use a large arsenal of weapons, from a ripping whip to a stunning shotgun, to customize your play style and mow down your enemies with efficiency.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/42ec45bc22882c08433cc1ce531b171e.poster.avif?t=1728411903\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/42ec45bc22882c08433cc1ce531b171e.webm?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/42ec45bc22882c08433cc1ce531b171e.mp4?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>About the developer — the game has been developed by one person for more than 3 years.<br><br></li><li>The duration of the game is 10-15 hours.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/3889602004228a69c1770d4527993acc.avif?t=1728411903\" width=610 height=130 /></span><br><br>Slash your way through Estencel! Traverse across a corrupted, maze like city fighting horrors. Customize and arm yourself into the ultimate monster killing assassin in this fast paced dark fantasy Action. Solve the mysteries of this world before they swallow you whole.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/1fcfa6da0cf27d22722ed8f716d9f135.poster.avif?t=1728411903\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/1fcfa6da0cf27d22722ed8f716d9f135.webm?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/1fcfa6da0cf27d22722ed8f716d9f135.mp4?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A Variety of Enemies — Choose your combat style against diverse opponents and defeat merciless bosses with your cunning wit.<br><br></li><li>Exploration — Traverse the city and its outskirts and discover what secrets hide in its shadows.<br><br></li><li>Online multiplayer - play with your friends in co-op for up to 8 people.<br> </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/9b2d1b458e1abf5cea2be42c43850495.poster.avif?t=1728411903\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/9b2d1b458e1abf5cea2be42c43850495.webm?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/9b2d1b458e1abf5cea2be42c43850495.mp4?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic Combat System — Upgrade your primary weapon or swap to your secondary to overwhelm your opponent.<br><br></li><li>Use a large arsenal of weapons, from a ripping whip to a stunning shotgun, to customize your play style and mow down your enemies with efficiency.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/42ec45bc22882c08433cc1ce531b171e.poster.avif?t=1728411903\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/42ec45bc22882c08433cc1ce531b171e.webm?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025320/extras/42ec45bc22882c08433cc1ce531b171e.mp4?t=1728411903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>About the developer — the game has been developed by one person for more than 3 years.<br><br></li><li>The duration of the game is 10-15 hours.</li></ul>",
